Last posts for a few hours. C ya then, everyone.

::Firearm/Rex/Kluster::

Firearm and Rex jump in opposite directions, the missile destroying a tree 
behind them. They get up, Firearm aiming his cannon at Chordate while Rex 
looks at Brix/Bronco/Octociz.

"Are you allright?" Rex asks.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Kluster recieves the transmission from Chordate. "I'm at an important 
meeting," he replies, "Can you take care of it?"
